room_title: Escape room "Virus" by Escape Hatch - Bixby in Tulsa
room_description: Blackmailed by a terrorist cell, Dr. Nettles was forced to turn over a vile of an extremely deadly virus. You - his staff - have discovered his secret on his computer and now you are in a race against time to find where the virus is hidden and contain it before it's released into the air. By the way, what happened to Dr. Nettles?
